{{Metaphor |Name gloss=MORALITY IS PURITY |Aliases={{Metaphor.Alias |Metaphor.Alias.Name=МОРАЛЬ - ЭТО ЧИСТОТА (НЕПОРОЧНОСТЬ) |Metaphor.Alias.Provenance=Metaphors We Live By, Philosophy in the Flesh }} |Family=Social Metaphors, |Metaphor Level=General |Metaphor Type=Composed/complex |Source frame=ЧИСТОТА (НЕПОРОЧНОСТЬ) |Target frame=МОРАЛЬ |Mappings= |Related metaphors= |Entailments= |Examples={{Example |Example.Language=Russian |Example.Text=Обливать друг друга грязью очень опасно. Некоторые люди не знают, где помыть свои руки после выборов.
|Example.Gloss=To pour each other (instr.case) mud very dangerous. Some people not know where to wash hands after elections. |Example.English translation=Throwing mud at each other is a very dangerous thing. Some people don’t know where to wash their hands after the elections
|Example.Provenance=kommersant.ru }}{{Example |Example.Language=Russian |Example.Text=Чиновники умывают руки - разрешение они дали, а отслеживать, как медицинское средство продается и используется, в их компетенцию не входит. |Example.Gloss=Officials wash hands - authorization they gave,and to track how remedy sells and is used, into their competence not enter. |Example.English translation=Officials are washing their hands - they gave the authorization, but tracking the way a remedy is sold and used doesn't fall within their competence. |Example.Provenance=medrelax.narod.ru/pribor.htm |Example.Comments=The set expression "to wash one's hands" is used in Russian to denote reluctance of a person to participate in smth bad or illegal, to emphasize he/she is innocent. It originates from the old tradition to wash one's hands and say loudly "I'm innocent" to prove he/she has nothing to do with a certain criminal act. }}{{Example |Example.Language=Russian |Example.Text=Моя совесть чиста перед моей семьей и народом. Но у них совесть грязная. Они осуждены за грязные проделки в своей профессиональной деятельности. |Example.Gloss=My conscience pure in front of my family and people. But they are convicted for dirty shenanigans in professional activity. |Example.English translation=My conscience is pure in front of my family and people. But they are convicted for dirty shenanigans in their professional activity. |Example.Provenance=ru.hrsu.org/archives/3548 }} |Entered by=Inna, |Status=in development |Investigated for=Russian }}

