{{Metaphor
|Name gloss=ACTION IS SELF-PROPELLED MOTION ALONG A PATH
|Aliases={{Metaphor.Alias
|Metaphor.Alias.Name=ACTION IS SELF-PROPELLED MOTION ALONG A PATH
|Metaphor.Alias.Provenance=PITF
|Metaphor.Alias.Page no=187
}}
|Family=Метафора структуры события (Event structure metaphor)
|Metaphor Level=General
|Metaphor Type=Primary
|Source frame=самоходнoе движение
|Target frame=действие
|Mappings={{Mapping
|Target=aктер (actor)
|Source=само-двигатель (self-mover)
}}{{Mapping
|Target=x-схема действий (action_x-schema)
|Source=x-схема самодвижения (self-motion_x-schema)
}}
|Related metaphors={{Related metaphor
|Related metaphor.Relation type=is a source subcase of
|Related metaphor.Name=ДЕЙСТВИЕ - ЭТО ДВИЖЕНИЕ ПО ПУТИ
|Related metaphor.Description=more specific source domain
}}
|Entailments={{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=Помощь действий (AidTo Action)
|Entailment.Source inference=помощь Движения (Aid To Movement)
|Entailment.Entailed metaphors=Помощь действий - это помощь Движения (Aid To Action Is Aid To Movement)
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=Manner Of Action
|Entailment.Source inference=Manner Of Movement
|Entailment.Entailed metaphors=Manner Of Action Is Manner Of Movement
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=Careful Action 
|Entailment.Source inference=Careful Movement
|Entailment.Entailed metaphors=Careful Action Is Careful Movement
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Entailed metaphors=Speed Of Action Is Speed Of Movement 
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Entailed metaphors=Freedom Of Action Is The Lack Of Impediment To Movement
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Entailed metaphors=Suspension Of Action Is The Stopping Of Movement
}}
|Examples={{Example
|Example.Language=Russian
|Example.Text=Ветер с юга, с южного российского берега, ― это ветер в паруса экономического сотрудничества сопредельных стран.
|Example.English translation=Wind from the south, from the southern Russian coast - is the wind in the sails of economic cooperation of neighboring countries.
|Example.Provenance=http://www.ruscorpora.ru/en/search-main.html
|Example.Comments=Помощь действий - это помощь Движения (Aid To Action Is Aid To Movement)
}}{{Example
|Example.Language=Russian
}}
